{"title":"旗","authors":["姚辉"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姚辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那片如火的空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们太熟悉了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几乎忘记她凝重的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂缀满星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每棵禾苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便又一次茂盛出热血的痕迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许不是每一种思想都来自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗　帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们是旗帜的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热爱旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有理由站在旗帜下微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们已开始懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自过去的风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有理由痛哭或者欣慰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了旗帜曾经有过的苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了那片灼满弹洞的星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了能贡献出自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请记住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使有人摆出种种“理由”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也不能拒绝从一双双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中接过那种嘱托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那种自豪"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}